# Notion Progress Tracking

Genie progress is tracked in Notion. Config: `.cursor/notion.json`. Skill: `notion-progress-tracking`.

## Hub

[Genie Platform — Engineering Hub](https://app.notion.com/p/391d48599a9981739d54d95dca415f29)

- **Genie Phases** — roadmap phases (1–10)
- **Genie Tasks** — implementation tasks linked to phases

## Required workflow

| Event | Notion action |
|-------|---------------|
| Start feature | Find/create task → Status `In progress` |
| Complete feature | Status `Done` (only after definition of done) |
| New scope | Create task with Phase, Priority, Area, Repo Path |
| Status request | Query Genie Tasks and report |

## Integration points

- **feature-implementation** skill — create/update task in Phase 1 of plan
- **project-manager** subagent — owns phase alignment and task breakdown in Notion
- **definition-of-done** — Done in Notion requires all DoD criteria met

Use Notion MCP server `plugin-notion-workspace-notion` for all updates.
